ract class, you have to inherit it from another class, provide implementations to the abstract methods in it. If you inherit an abstract class, you have to provide implementations to all the abstract methods in it. Example This section provides you an example of the abstract class. To create an abstract class, just use the abstract keyword before the class keyword, in the class declaration. 
